						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2012/01/boo.html" title="19:22" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-01-07T19:22:07+00:00" pubdate>January 7, 2012</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
