				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/12/the-big-dig-journalism-conference-copenhagen.html" title="19:50" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2011-12-22T19:50:59+00:00" pubdate>December 22, 2011</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
