		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/10/speaking-at-mediafabric-conference-prague-21-october.html" title="Permalink to Speaking at Mediafabric Conference, Prague, 21 October" rel="bookmark">Speaking at Mediafabric Conference, Prague, 21 October</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/10/speaking-at-mediafabric-conference-prague-21-october.html" title="17:53" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2011-10-19T17:53:22+00:00" pubdate>October 19, 2011</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/10/speaking-at-mediafabric-conference-prague-21-october.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/6a00e55090303188330153926e36c4970b-popup.html" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="float: left;"><img alt="SF_brandmark_small" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00e55090303188330153926e36c4970b" src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/6a00e55090303188330153926e36c4970b-120wi.jpg" style="margin: 0px 5px 5px 0px;" title="SF_brandmark_small" /></a></p>
<p>Off tomor­row to speak at the <a href="http://conference.sourcefabric.org/" target="_self">Medi­afab­ric</a> con­fer­ence in Prague. </p>
<p>Should be a good one — all about the media, journ­al­ists, tech­no­lo­gists, design­ers, hack­ers,  and all points in between!</p>
<p>The con­fer­ence has been organ­ised by <a href="http://www.sourcefabric.org/" target="_self">Source­fab­ric</a>, and there will be live stream­ing <a href="http://livestream.com/sourcefabric" target="_self">here</a>.</p>
