				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gijc" rel="tag">gijc</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/journalism" rel="tag">journalism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/law-2" rel="tag">law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/machon" rel="tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/media-2" rel="tag">media</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/osa" rel="tag">OSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>			</span>
						
