	<article id="post-27" class="post-27 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-books category-film category-intelligence category-interviews category-machon category-media category-mi6 category-spies category-tv tag-cinepolitics tag-films tag-intelligence-2 tag-le-carre tag-machon tag-mi6 tag-spies-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/10/review-of-tinker-tailor-soldier-spy.html" title="Permalink to Review of “Tinker, Tailor, Soldier, Spy”" rel="bookmark">Review of “Tinker, Tailor, Soldier, Spy”</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/10/review-of-tinker-tailor-soldier-spy.html" title="19:54" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2011-10-17T19:54:03+00:00" pubdate>October 17, 2011</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/10/review-of-tinker-tailor-soldier-spy.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>A review on “Cinepol­it­ics” of the new film of <a href="http://www.johnlecarre.com/news/2011/10/11/watch-tinker-tailor-soldier-spy-discussed-on-cine-politics" target="_self">John Le Carre’s</a> clas­sic spy novel, and its con­tinu­ing relevance:</p>
<p><iframe frameborder="0" height="360" src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/30585624" width="448"></iframe></p>
<p> </p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/10/review-of-tinker-tailor-soldier-spy.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
